C-a c   - new window
C-a ,   - rename window
C-a f   - find window
C-a n   - next window
C-a p   - previous window
C-a &   - kill window
C-a w   - list windows
C-a z   - maximize pane (zoom)
C-a +   - Break pane to window
C-a -   - Restore pane from window
C-a q   - Show pane numbers
C-a t	- Big clock
C-a C-h, C-j... - Resize pane
